One can run the test-
1.from editor from testSuites folder and running as TestNG Suite
2.From command prompt by using command mvn test clean or
mvn test -PTenforce where -P indicates profile and Tenforce is the profile name given in pom.xml


Used testNG framework as it is easier to control execution and group tests

Have used POM model with BaseTest and BasePage(Abstract Component) classes
Can optimise the code further to put Javascript executor in reusable method.
